{"tid":1006867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生化危機2】淘寶賣家改名避查 呢批「暗號」超搞笑！","createTime":"2019-02-03T10:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T10:24:39.000Z","uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4717f88a38fb911cba85bc81d983b5be0cc7928","tid":1006867,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"內地打擊暴力血腥電子遊戲，即使近日大熱的《生化危機2》（Resident Evil 2）高畫質重製版也受到封殺。不過，內地淘寶賣家就用「暗號」避過當局審查，例如把遊戲名稱改為《我來警察局上班第一天重製版》、《炒冷飯2》、《打怪2重製版》等等，務求將遊戲「重出生天」。<br />\n《生化危機2》原本是1998年的作品，睽違21年，又以完全高畫質重新製作，全球首周售出300萬套。這次重製版除了繁、簡體中文外，還原漢語配音版。不過，國家文化部認為遊戲「有害國家安全」，以及「血腥暴力」等原因，遭全面禁止販售。<br />\n淘寶賣家則各展身手，用暗號將遊戲上架，商品配圖也相當有創意，網民留言寫道：「《我來警局上班的第一天》重製版。嗯......遊戲裏的內容就是主角到拉昆市（浣熊市）警局上班第一天的過程沒錯，算你過。而且居然還有可愛小插畫，真是太不血腥暴力了。」「《打怪2重製版》......好啦，雖然看起來像甚麼很不好玩的手機遊戲，至少圖案上有殭屍嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190202/59215709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59215709&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7kBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=2872a77a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59215709&h=39d68282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190202/59215709</a><br />\n<br />\n網民講乜：<br />\nShenzhenwd：《我來警局上班的第一天》就遇上了城市末日這件事，真的沒問題嗎？<br />\n洛小跑：哈哈哈哈哈美工也厲害了！！<br />\n吉吉--LEE：這個遊戲還有很多藝名，《炒冷飯2重製》，《大作2重製》。<br />\n夢中醒不過來：看評論才知道是啥遊戲<br />\nQuarth：不改名字沒法賣<br />\n<br />\n支那豬連Bio都唔比打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376ac7bb5ffbd4df7f302d5592ff27943ba0a31f","tid":1006867,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpG1uGk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpG1uGk.jpg&h=0e0bf8dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybVYwUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybVYwUG.jpg&h=a095daa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fCTkN1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fCTkN1.jpg&h=48ba8e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61db3930bd969c917e4fef0cd4ce7119f8823ba4","tid":1006867,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"香港人而家都冇呢D創意"},{"pid":"89ae4b5cc716e25f06bd0bcd65423c715011c8a1","tid":1006867,"uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61db3930bd969c917e4fef0cd4ce7119f8823ba4","tid":1006867,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"香港人而家都冇呢D創意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"香港人有得玩洗咩改到咁"}]}